    lessonInLife:
      "The great spiritual lesson of Capricorn is learning that they are not what they build, not what they achieve, and not what the world sees when it looks at their accomplishments. They are here to discover that the mountain they have been climbing all their life was never the point — the point was who they became during the climb. And the ultimate summit is not success, or wealth, or legacy, but the quiet, unshakable knowledge that they are worthy of love, rest, and peace — not because they earned it but because they were always, from the very beginning, enough.",
